::Aerotaur::
    He slowly came out of his daze and exited the CR chamber.  He felt better 
now that his mech fluid had replenished itself.  He looked down at his chest 
and saw that the cuts had healed.  He walks over to where Nightlight is 
holding Trinity.  "What's going on?" he asks when he sees the concern on her 
face.
